            <title>[QPID-4017] AMQP 0-9: Failover causes flow control blocked flag to get stuck </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-4017</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When testing failover with a single broker, we observed problems if a session is currently blocked due to flow control. Following the broker restart, the session is reestablished but it remains blocked forever.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is to reset the blocked flag during failover. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
